name: 吉安·扬森斯
introduction: Jean Janssens was born on February 7, 1999 in Herentals. Jean grew up in the Kempen and now lives in Antwerp. Jean studied Human Sciences in secondary school, then Military Sciences at the Military School in Brussels and then Psychology in Antwerp. Jean interrupted this training in 2018 to further develop their talent as an actor.You may know Jean Janssens from the TV series Campus 12 (2018-2020), the TV series Lisa (2020-2022) and the TV series Gamekeepers (2021-2023).Besides acting, Jean plays football in competitions and is busy making their own music and photography.
